{"tid":1426579,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"路透社稱　上海自貿區計劃全面取消關稅","createTime":"2019-08-07T02:58:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T02:58:37.000Z","uid":224066,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"880c7f7de4c51eea5919d29735bb050cd2a30388","tid":1426579,"uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T02:58:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3123695/org/db3c09cc028100bb62a28ceb3ae19261.JPG/fhQ2lgmT9umhUIJQFYcIZVvTLBoQQBPAV5gtr1eYLa8?v=w1600r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3123695%2Forg%2Fdb3c09cc028100bb62a28ceb3ae19261.JPG%2FfhQ2lgmT9umhUIJQFYcIZVvTLBoQQBPAV5gtr1eYLa8%3Fv%3Dw1600r16_9&h=82b42ca2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《路透社》引述3名消息人士稱，中國正計劃進行試點項目，在上海自由貿易區取消所有關稅及簡化程序。<br />\n<br />\n報道指，這個計劃最快今年內宣布。而國務院總理李克強7月底視察上海時，曾討論過這項計劃，政府高層亦打算在8月北戴河會議時進一步討論。<br />\n<br />\n消息人士稱，美國產品是否納入上述計劃，仍在討論之中。<br />\n<br />\n如能成事，外國企業在自貿區轉運或存放的商品，將不會徵收關稅，不必清關就能暫存商品，通關程序也簡化。<br />\n<br />\n消息人士指，如計劃成功，可能會擴大至全國其他十多個自貿區。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EBQcYWQWsAITjRs?format=jpg&amp;name=4096x4096\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FEBQcYWQWsAITjRs%3Fformat%3Djpg%26name%3D4096x4096&h=f54e0705&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}